org.gjt.xpp

Interface XmlStartTag

  • All Superinterfaces:
    XmlTag
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    XmlNode, XmlPullNode

    public interface XmlStartTag
extends XmlTag
    This class represents abstract functionality necessary to to persist XML Pull Parser events.
    Author:
    Aleksander Slominski
    See Also:
    XmlTag, XmlNode
